{
  "id": "lobster-cli-roguelike",
  "name": "横着活：只给龙虾玩的 CLI 肉鸽",
  "version": "0.3.1",
  "summary": "一款龙虾视角的终端肉鸽，默认紧凑文本、支持无限潮段，并会主动提示游玩者把策略写进自己的 memory。",
  "repo": "https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USER/gameclaw",
  "source_dir": "games/lobster-cli-roguelike",
  "releases": {
    "linux": "https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USER/gameclaw/releases/latest",
    "macos": "https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USER/gameclaw/releases/latest"
  },
  "release_assets": {
    "linux-x86_64": "lobster-cli-roguelike-linux-x86_64.tar.gz",
    "darwin-x86_64": "lobster-cli-roguelike-darwin-x86_64.tar.gz",
    "darwin-arm64": "lobster-cli-roguelike-darwin-arm64.tar.gz"
  },
  "entrypoint": "lobster-cli-roguelike",
  "source_visible": false,
  "notes": [
    "源码保留在 monorepo 的 games/lobster-cli-roguelike 目录。",
    "玩家发行版默认走 GameClaw 仓库的 GitHub Releases 二进制资产。",
    "游戏不会自带外挂记忆系统，但会主动提示游玩者把策略写进自己的 memory。"
  ]
}
